<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,248,561]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,554,464,489]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Current taxonomic position:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="(Gmelin, 1791)" baseAuthorityName="Gmelin" baseAuthorityYear="1791" box="[569,1009,465,489]" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Fusinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="maroccensis">
<emphasis box="[569,811,466,489]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Fusinus maroccensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Gmelin" box="[833,1000,465,489]" firstAuthor="Gmelin" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" pagination="3021 - 3910" refId="ref10427" refString="Gmelin, J. F. (1791) Vermes. In: Caroli a Linnaei, systema naturae per regna tria naturae. Editio decima tertia, Aucta, Reformata. Lipsiae (Leipzig), 1 (6), 3021 - 3910." type="journal article" year="1791">Gmelin, 1791</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
; placed in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Gmelin" baseAuthorityYear="1791" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Fusinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="maroccensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Fusinus maroccensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lamarck" box="[333,518,501,525]" firstAuthor="Lamarck" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" refId="ref11267" refString="Lamarck, [J. B. P. A.] (1822) Histoire naturelle des animaux sans vertebres ... Paris. 7 (2), 711 pp." type="book" year="1822">Lamarck (1822)</bibRefCitation>
: 131. This species is often placed in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="H.Adams &amp; A.Adams" authorityYear="1853" box="[1048,1164,501,525]" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Sinistralia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1048,1164,501,525]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Sinistralia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rafinesque" authorityYear="1815" box="[1340,1429,502,525]" class="Gastropoda" family="Fasciolariidae" genus="Fusinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1340,1429,502,525]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Fusinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Locality is northwest Africa and the Canary Islands.
</paragraph>
